## Versioning Documentation

### When to Update Version

- **Major (X.0):** Breaking changes, major reorganization
- **Minor (X.Y):** New sections, significant additions
- **Patch:** Usually not used for docs

### Update Checklist

When updating docs:
- [ ] Update "Last Updated" with current timestamp (EST)
- [ ] Increment version if significant change
- [ ] Update cross-references if structure changed
- [ ] Review for accuracy and completeness

